</div>
<div id="attachment_245658" style="width: 1466px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-245658" class="wp-image-245658 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/rubio-10-e1714054893163.jpg" alt="a glass bead-coated spherical sculpture made from a basketball depicting a woman on horseback, wearing a crown, on a white background" width="1456" height="1440" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/rubio-10-e1714054893163.jpg 1456w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/rubio-10-e1714054893163-640x633.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/rubio-10-e1714054893163-960x949.jpg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 1456px) 100vw, 1456px"></p>
